value:
Fascicles "10" and "11" from the full score (the rest of which is at GB Lbl R.M.29.b.12), from the beginning of HWV 8a, no. 17 - to the middle of HWV 8a, no. 20.
Editorial title.
Holograph manuscript in ink.
Watermark: p. 17-18, 23-24: "LVG" below fleur de lis over Strasbourg bend; countermark: "IV" (Burrows C12.5)
Watermark: p. 19-22: Fleur de lis over Strasbourg bend ; countermark "CDG" (Burrows D30)
Watermarks: p. 25-32: Fleur de lis over Strasbourg bend ; countermark "IV" (Burrows B10)
Contents:
